main event: A civilian observed a round object with a reddish glow and white blinking lights in Bremerton, Washington.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 10 to 15 seconds., The object was described as being the size of a volleyball., The object was located 20 degrees above the horizon., No photographs were included with the report., The object was moving on a northeastern course.
sighted object: a round object with a reddish glow and white blinking lights
